citation: Inland Fisheries (Seasons and Waters) Amendment Order 2007 (Rescinded) (Tas)
text:
Inland Fisheries (Seasons and Waters) Amendment Order 2007 (Rescinded)

This Statutory Rule has been rescinded.

1. (Rescinded)
    The Inland Fisheries (Seasons and Waters) Amendment Order 2007 have been rescinded by Schedule 3 to the Redundant Legislation Repeal Act 2016
